Claims_Details_Ola

As soon as the claim is generated and there are no documents or risk/vlaue associated with the claim, the task is triggered.
Call center agent will perform this task and call the customer for claim details.

tid
claim_details_call_ola

worker_role
call_center_agent

conditions
claim_id = generated and documents_uploaded = NO

assignment_Logic
agent who generated claim_id 

post_hook
IF document_uploaded = NO and current_time - claim_generated_time > 6 hrs

SMS to customer
Hi, this is a gentle reminder for you to upload the required documents on the ola app for further processing of <policy_id> associated with Ola trip <CRN/Tripid>.
You can also mail the same documents to <mail id> and we can take the process further.

Email to customer
Hi <CustomerName>,

This is a gentle reminder for you to upload the required documents on the ola app for further processing of <policy_id> associated with Ola trip <CRN/Tripid>.
You can go to Choose an issue ----> Claim insurance -----> select the type of claim you want ------> Upload the documents. And its done.
We would further process your claim and get it processed as soon as possible.

Thanks Team Acko

