Approver: Assess car and document photos

tid
approval_process

worker_role
inspection-approver

conditions
preinspection_status= approval_pending

assignment_Logic
evenly distributed amongst approvers who are online

post_hooks
If preinspection_status=approval_done and policy_status = approved.

 If damage status of one or more car parts is not intact, include them in exclusions.
Email/SMS will also include list of missing required documents.
- SMS to customer
Hi <CustomerName>, Your vehicle’s inspection is approved. You can download report here {link}. You can pay by clicking on this link {link}

- Email to customer
Hi <salutation><CustomerName>

Your vehicle’s inspection is approved. You can download report here {link}. Y ou can use the following link {link} to make payment.

Thanks Team Acko <Include customer toll free number in signature>

If preinspection_status=approval_done and policy_status=rejected.

SMS to customer:: Your vehicle’s inspection is approved. You can download report here {link}. Your refund has been initiated, it will be credited back to your account within X working days

Email to customer::

Hi <Salutation><CustomerName>

Your vehicle’s inspection is not approved. You can download the inspection report here {link}.

Thanks Team Acko <Include customer toll free number in signature>

If preinspection_status=approval_done and policy_status = rejected.

SMS to customer:: We are sorry to inform your vehicle’s inspection is not approved. You can download report here {link}.

Email to customer::

Hi <Salutation><CustomerName>

We are sorry to inform your vehicle’s inspection is not approved. You can download the inspection report here {link}.

Thanks Team Acko <Include customer toll free number in signature>

